121
00:07:12,690 --> 00:07:17,679
Myslela som si, že ma posiela domov, lebo ma nechce.

122
00:07:17,679 --> 00:07:19,629
Ale dokonca ostane na noc.

123
00:07:19,629 --> 00:07:21,119
